# Department Highest Salary

## Problem Summary
Write a query to find the employee(s) with the highest salary in each department.

## Solution
```sql
SELECT
    d.name AS department,
    e.name AS employee,
    e.salary AS salary
FROM Employee e
JOIN Department d
    ON e.departmentId = d.id
WHERE e.salary = (
    SELECT MAX(salary)
    FROM Employee
    WHERE departmentId = e.departmentId
);
```
